content.text: Hey there! I'm a member of four book clubs, the PTA, and two book groups. How about you?
I took some time off to travel and explore my interests.
That sounds like a lot of fun! What did you do?
I went to Japan and France. I spent a lot of time eating good food.
That's great! I love to travel too. I've never been to Japan or France, but I've been to a few other countries.
I have a pet snake.
Oh cool! What kind of snake?
It's a corn snake.
I've never heard of a corn snake.
They're pretty cool snakes. They're not very big, and they're pretty easy to take care of.
That sounds like a great pet.
It is. I love having him around.
I'm glad to hear that.
So, what do you do for a living?
I'm a lawyer.
Oh, cool! I've always thought about going to law school.
It's a lot of work, but it's also a lot of fun.
Do you like it?
I do. I like helping people, and I like the challenge of the work.
That's great! It sounds like you have a pretty good job.
I do. I'm lucky to be doing what I love.
